item.title: Information Model Documentation Portal
item.description: Go directly to the documentation portal Introduction The models are designed and documented in Enterprise Architect (EA). You can find the EA project at https://github.com/FINTprosjektet/fint-informasjonsmodell. Documentation portal For a more userfriendly view of the models we developet a frontend to the XMI 2.1 export from EA. You can find the documentation portal at https://informasjonsmodell.felleskomponent.no. The project for the frontend is found here. Contribute If you find bugs or have suggestions for improvement please feel free to submit an issue.
